---

<Layout title="Glen's Portfolio | Home">
	<IpodPortfolio
		pages={{
			home: '<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Welcome</h1>...',
			resume: '<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">My Resume</h1>...',
			project1: `<div class="space-y-12">
  <div class="mb-16 portfolio-section">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6 portfolio-text">Magic Mirror</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl portfolio-text">Magic Mirror is a hypothetical interface for a full-length mirror that helps users plan outfits by integrating weather, schedule, and closet management. As a UX designer, I focused on simplifying the outfit-planning process and improving usability through iterative design.</p>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mt-4 portfolio-text">Users struggled with planning outfits due to unpredictable weather and busy schedules. Our goal was to create a seamless way to visualize outfits, check weather, and plan ahead.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="portfolio-section">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 portfolio-text">Audience</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl portfolio-text">With this in mind we considered who our audience would be and why they would use this product.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 my-12">
    <div class="portfolio-image portfolio-image-left">
      <img src="https://placehold.co/400x500?text=Persona+1" alt="User Persona 1" class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-lg" />
      <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mt-4 text-sm">Persona Research</p>
    </div>
    <div class="portfolio-image portfolio-image-right">
      <img src="https://placehold.co/400x500?text=Persona+2" alt="User Persona 2" class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-lg" />
      <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mt-4 text-sm">Target Users</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="portfolio-section">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 portfolio-text">Competitive Analysis</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl portfolio-text">We did a competitive analysis to see what other options on the market had to offer, and what opportunities we could take advantage of.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="my-12 portfolio-image portfolio-image-left">
    <img src="https://placehold.co/800x400?text=Competitive+Analysis" alt="Competitive Analysis" class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-lg" />
    <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mt-4 text-sm">Market Opportunities</p>
  </div>

  <div class="portfolio-section mt-16">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 portfolio-text">Brainstorming</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl portfolio-text">These are a few sketches we did to get our ideas to feel more tangible. Sketching is great because it allows me to get my ideas out fast without worrying about pixel perfection.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="my-12 space-y-6">
